            "1 2024-10-25  STR_103          Delhi    PRD_492           Sports   \n",
            "2 2023-02-28  STR_107        Kolkata    PRD_958        Groceries   \n",
            "3 2023-06-16  STR_102      Bangalore    PRD_014  Home Appliances   \n",
