            "0    Debit Card                Yes           422          4.4  South   \n",
            "1           UPI                 No           302          4.1  North   \n",
            "2          Cash                 No           184          3.8   East   \n",
            "3           UPI                Yes           493          3.7  South   \n",
            "4   Credit Card                 No           359          3.5   West   \n",
            "\n",
